  m_text: "Hello, welcome to Fortuna!\r\n\r\nThank you for logging into Fortuna.
    \nWe would like to share a few important reminders and information:\r\n\r\nUsername
    and Password: \nPlease make sure you keep your username and password \nin a safe
    place. If you forget, you will not be able to access it.\r\n\r\nAccount Deletion
    Policy: \ndoes not take care to use sections regularly.\nNote that if you do
    not log in for 7 days (1 week),\nyour account may be deleted for security reasons.\r\n\r\nSponsorship
    Status: \nFortuna application was implemented as a\nresult of an independent
    improvement process. \nIt is not sponsored by either the Play Store or the App
    Store. \nOur aim is to provide the best experience \nand to expand the dimension
    continuously.\r\n\r\nDeveloper Follow: \nYou can follow Omeryavus,\nthe developer
    of the application,\non Instagram and YouTube platforms. \nIn this way, you can
    take a closer \nlook at improvements and updates.\r\n\r\nWith Fortuna, \nyou
    have the opportunity to earn money \njust by clicking the button! You can get
    \nbigger prizes by spending the money \nyou earn in other games of chance.\r\n\r\nThanks
    again for applying, \ngood luck and a fun experience!"
